<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="351" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="18.[130,777,216,784]" box="[132,232,216,242]" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">REMARKS</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="18.[130,777,216,784]" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">
The study of the 
<typeStatus box="[325,372,248,274]" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">type</typeStatus>
material showed that 
<taxonomicName authority="Thiele, 1925" authorityName="Thiele" authorityYear="1925" baseAuthorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" baseAuthorityYear="1925" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Rissoa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="hertzogi">
<emphasis box="[620,775,247,273]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">Rissoa hertzogi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Thiele" box="[132,270,279,306]" firstAuthor="Thiele" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" pagination="35 - 382" refId="ref34767" refString="THIELE J. 1925. - Gastropoden der Deutschen Tiefsee-Expedition. II Teil. Wissenschaftliche Ergebnisse der Deutschen TiefseeExpedition auf dem Dampfer &quot; Valdivia &quot; 1898 - 1899: 17 (2): 35 - 382, pls 13 - 46 [reprints paginated 1 - 348, pls 1 - 34]." type="journal article" year="1925">Thiele, 1925</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation box="[286,352,279,305]" captionStart="FIG" captionStartId="17.[132,143,1985,2003]" captionTargetBox="[132,1455,215,1877]" captionTargetId="figure-92@17.[131,795,768,1324]" captionTargetPageId="17" captionText="FIG. 7. — Benthonellania hertzogi (Thiele,1925),syntypes,Valdivia Stn 109 (ZMB–64981):A-C, syntype,height 2.85 mm (ZMB-64981);D-F, syntype,height 2.47 mm (ZMB-64981); G, original label; H, original drawings (Thiele 1925, 82, pl. 6, fig. 15, 16); I, J, syntype (A-C), detail of the first whorls. Scale bars: I, J: 0.25 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6794860" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6794860/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">Figs 7</figureCitation>
A-J; 9A, B) and 
<taxonomicName authority="Thiele, 1925" authorityName="Thiele" authorityYear="1925" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Rissoa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="africana">
<emphasis box="[536,692,279,305]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">Rissoa africana</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Thiele" firstAuthor="Thiele" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" pagination="35 - 382" refId="ref34767" refString="THIELE J. 1925. - Gastropoden der Deutschen Tiefsee-Expedition. II Teil. Wissenschaftliche Ergebnisse der Deutschen TiefseeExpedition auf dem Dampfer &quot; Valdivia &quot; 1898 - 1899: 17 (2): 35 - 382, pls 13 - 46 [reprints paginated 1 - 348, pls 1 - 34]." type="journal article" year="1925">Thiele, 1925</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation box="[206,272,311,337]" captionStart="FIG" captionStartId="19.[132,143,1962,1980]" captionTargetBox="[130,1456,216,1882]" captionTargetId="figure-15@19.[130,1456,216,1946]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIG. 8. — Benthonellania africana (Thiele,1925) n. comb.: A-C, lectotype, height 3.85 mm; D-F, paralectotype height 3.7 mm; G-I, paralectotype,height 3.35 mm; Valdivia Stn 251, ZMB–64955; J, K, paralectotype, detail of the first whorls; L, original label; M, original drawing (Thiele 1925, 83, pl. 6, fig. 20); N, paralectotype, detail of the teleoconch sculpture spiral on the last whorl. Valdivia Stn 251, ZMB–64955. Scale bars: J, K, N, 0.50 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6794862" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6794862/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">Figs 8</figureCitation>
A-N; 9C, D) belong to this genus, with their paucispiral protoconchs devoid of spiral sculpture. Both species are very similar to e.g. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bouchet &amp; Waren" authorityYear="1993" box="[379,514,375,401]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="agastachys">
<emphasis box="[379,514,375,401]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">B. agastachys</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="R. B. Watson" baseAuthorityYear="1886" box="[528,653,375,401]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="fayalensis">
<emphasis box="[528,653,375,401]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">B. fayalensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bouchet &amp; Waren" authorityYear="1993" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="oligostigma">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">B. oligostigma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with their slender shell and the crown of adapical thickening of axials, enhanced by the subsutural depression. We proposed thus, 
<taxonomicName authority="(Thiele, 1925)" authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Thiele" baseAuthorityYear="1925" box="[352,775,470,497]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="hertzogi" status="n. comb.">
<emphasis box="[352,606,470,496]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">Benthonellania hertzogi</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Thiele" box="[623,767,470,497]" firstAuthor="Thiele" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" pagination="35 - 382" refId="ref34767" refString="THIELE J. 1925. - Gastropoden der Deutschen Tiefsee-Expedition. II Teil. Wissenschaftliche Ergebnisse der Deutschen TiefseeExpedition auf dem Dampfer &quot; Valdivia &quot; 1898 - 1899: 17 (2): 35 - 382, pls 13 - 46 [reprints paginated 1 - 348, pls 1 - 34]." type="journal article" year="1925">Thiele, 1925</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[134,228,502,529]" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" rank="species">n. comb.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="(Thiele, 1925)" authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Thiele" baseAuthorityYear="1925" box="[276,676,502,529]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="africana" status="n. comb.">
<emphasis box="[276,521,502,528]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">Benthonellania africana</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Thiele" box="[533,669,502,529]" firstAuthor="Thiele" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" pagination="35 - 382" refId="ref34767" refString="THIELE J. 1925. - Gastropoden der Deutschen Tiefsee-Expedition. II Teil. Wissenschaftliche Ergebnisse der Deutschen TiefseeExpedition auf dem Dampfer &quot; Valdivia &quot; 1898 - 1899: 17 (2): 35 - 382, pls 13 - 46 [reprints paginated 1 - 348, pls 1 - 34]." type="journal article" year="1925">Thiele, 1925</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[681,776,502,529]" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" rank="species">n. comb.</taxonomicNameLabel>
as new combinations for 
<taxonomicName authority="Thiele, 1925" authorityName="Thiele" authorityYear="1925" baseAuthorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" baseAuthorityYear="1925" box="[394,682,534,561]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Rissoa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="hertzogi">
<emphasis box="[394,543,534,560]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">Rissoa hertzogi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Thiele" box="[548,682,534,561]" firstAuthor="Thiele" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" pagination="35 - 382" refId="ref34767" refString="THIELE J. 1925. - Gastropoden der Deutschen Tiefsee-Expedition. II Teil. Wissenschaftliche Ergebnisse der Deutschen TiefseeExpedition auf dem Dampfer &quot; Valdivia &quot; 1898 - 1899: 17 (2): 35 - 382, pls 13 - 46 [reprints paginated 1 - 348, pls 1 - 34]." type="journal article" year="1925">Thiele, 1925</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Thiele, 1925" authorityName="Thiele" authorityYear="1925" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Rissoa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="africana">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">Rissoa africana</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Thiele" box="[263,402,566,593]" firstAuthor="Thiele" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" pagination="35 - 382" refId="ref34767" refString="THIELE J. 1925. - Gastropoden der Deutschen Tiefsee-Expedition. II Teil. Wissenschaftliche Ergebnisse der Deutschen TiefseeExpedition auf dem Dampfer &quot; Valdivia &quot; 1898 - 1899: 17 (2): 35 - 382, pls 13 - 46 [reprints paginated 1 - 348, pls 1 - 34]." type="journal article" year="1925">Thiele, 1925</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, respectively.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="18.[130,777,216,784]" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Thiele" baseAuthorityYear="1925" box="[155,400,598,624]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="hertzogi" status="n. comb.">
<emphasis box="[155,400,598,624]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">Benthonellania hertzogi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[406,502,598,624]" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" rank="species">n. comb.</taxonomicNameLabel>
differs from 
<taxonomicName authority="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio, 2022" authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" box="[639,775,598,624]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="basistriata" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[639,775,598,624]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">B. basistriata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[132,188,630,656]" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
paucispiral vs multispiral protoconch, in its less canaliculated sutures, its tight umbilical chink, absent in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" box="[635,767,662,688]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="basistriata">
<emphasis box="[635,767,662,688]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">B. basistriata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, more numerous axial ribs (24-26 vs 
<quantity box="[522,616,693,720]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.318" metricValueMax="5.08" metricValueMin="3.556" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" unit="in" value="17.0" valueMax="20.0" valueMin="14.0">14-20 in</quantity>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" box="[623,759,693,719]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="basistriata">
<emphasis box="[623,759,693,719]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">B. basistriata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="18.[130,777,216,784]" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">
See under 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Thiele" baseAuthorityYear="1925" box="[270,519,725,752]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="africana" status="n. comb.">
<emphasis box="[270,519,725,752]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">Benthonellania africana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[528,625,725,752]" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" rank="species">n. comb.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio, 2022" authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" box="[681,775,725,751]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="thielei" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[681,775,725,751]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="351">B. thielei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[132,191,758,784]" pageId="18" pageNumber="351" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
for diagnostic comparison.
</paragraph>
